title: SIC! SIC! SIC!
html:
SIC! SIC! SIC!

“Asked about social needs, Burdette said, 'Our safety net has a lot of holes in it.' ” [From the Parkersburg (West Virginia) News, 30 October 1986. Submitted by Glade Little, Parkersburg.]
